data.description: This BEAUTIFUL 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is Like New and MOVE-IN ready!! The open concept offers such a great flow. You will enter into a spacious foyer, with the two extra bedrooms and bath on the left and then into a large open living area, boasting a ton of natural light. The kitchen offers an 8-foot-long island, pendant lights, serving bar and walk-in pantry. The primary suite includes a private bath with dual vanities and a walk-in shower. The two-car garage doubles as a man-cave! The owners have taken immaculate care of the home and have added tinting to ALL windows (lower electric bills), ceiling fans in bedrooms, along with a beautifully sodded backyard. This newer community has so much to offer, including a (two) 9-hole golf course, a community pool and clubhouse in progress. Easy access to Hwy 59 and Hwy 105. Great private location with the conveniences of living in town.
